{"title":"美国“民主”大展览","authors":["天马　江有生"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":5,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国“民主”大展览"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　江有生画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上有飞机盘旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下有警察壮胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国世界博览会开幕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊前去讲演。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博览会展览什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有什么最值得看看？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你聪明猜不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百闻不如一见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是猩猩作画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是女人摔跤表演，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是人和兽比赛唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是打喷嚏唱片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是看谁钢琴砸得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是比赛哭泣和抽烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你聪明猜不着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百闻不如一见！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊在台上讲演："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个，这个，一二三……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑人在场外示威："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们的苦况展览给大家看！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊在台上讲演："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由、民主、人权……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警察在台下抓人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警棍、手铐、催泪弹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节目真精彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当场作表演！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博览会什么最值得看？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这就是答案！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}